# Architecture Rules вЂ” Menu Grading Tool (Databricks App)

## Deployment Model
- **Runtime**: Databricks Apps (serverless container, no Docker control)
- **Backend**: FastAPI on Python 3.11, served by uvicorn
- **Frontend**: React 18 + TypeScript + Vite, built to static files served by FastAPI
- **Entry point**: `src/app.py` вЂ” single process, must start with `python src/app.py`

## Tech Stack (Locked)
| Layer | Technology |
|-------|-----------|
| Backend | FastAPI (Python 3.11), uvicorn |
| Frontend | React 18, TypeScript, Vite, Tailwind CSS, shadcn/ui |
| State | Zustand (global), TanStack Query (server) |
| Charts | Recharts |
| Icons | Lucide React |
| PDF Parsing | pdf.js (text), Google Vision API (OCR) |
| AI/LLM | Anthropic Claude API (primary) |
| Excel Parsing | openpyxl (Python) |
| Square API | square Python SDK |
| Database | Delta Lake (SQL Warehouse) for persistent data |
| Auth | Databricks SSO (headers: X-Forwarded-Email, X-Forwarded-User) |
| Email | Resend (transactional email) |
| Fuzzy Match | fuzzywuzzy (Python) |

## NO-GO List
- вќЊ Docker / docker-compose (Databricks Apps handles container)
- вќЊ Redis / Memcached
- вќЊ Celery / RabbitMQ / Kafka
- вќЊ WebSockets (use SSE if needed)
- вќЊ SQLAlchemy ORM (use raw parameterized SQL for Delta Lake)
- вќЊ Next.js / Remix (use Vite + React SPA)
- вќЊ CSS-in-JS libraries (use Tailwind)
- вќЊ PostgreSQL as primary DB (use Delta Lake)
- вќЊ NextAuth.js (use Databricks SSO headers)

## API Conventions
- All endpoints under `/api/v1/`
- RESTful: GET (list/detail), POST (create), PUT (update), DELETE
- All responses: `{ "data": ..., "meta": {...} }` or `{ "error": ..., "detail": ... }`
- Pagination: `?page=1&page_size=20`

